REM Title: Battery + power status
REM Author: Cypher
REM Description: Shows charge %, cycle count, and AC/battery source. Useful
REM on laptops where the menu-bar percentage is hidden.
REM Target: macOS
DELAY 500
GUI SPACE
DELAY 500
STRING Terminal
DELAY 1000
ENTER
DELAY 800
STRING pmset -g batt; echo; ioreg -rn AppleSmartBattery | grep -E 'CycleCount|MaxCapacity|DesignCapacity' | head -3
ENTER
